  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The model was revised in early 2026 to incorporate updated impeller geometry and revised blood viscosity correlations; however, the primary rheology dataset used to parameterise the hemolysis sub-model carries a dataVintage of 2025-09-15, predating the modelRevisionDate of 2026-01-20. Re-validation against the post-revision model build is described as planned but has not been completed, leaving an epistemic gap in the currency of the input data.",
