    "rationale": "The assessment team accepted the package at Low assurance level for the purpose of informing iterative design decisions, acknowledging that all 13 credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels and that six factors carry epistemic gaps. The primary outstanding concern is the currency of hemolysis model input data: the rheology parameterisation dataset (dataVintage 2025-09-15) predates the January 2026 model revision, and re-validation is planned but not yet complete. Acceptance is conditional on completion of re-validation against the revised model build prior to any regulatory submission.",
